com.sebuilder.interpreter
Class Script

java.lang.Object
  com.sebuilder.interpreter.Script

public class Script
extends java.lang.Object

A Selenium 2 script. To create and run a test, instantiate a Script object, add some Script.Steps to its steps, then invoke "run". If you want to be able to run the script step by step, invoke "start", which will return a TestRun object.
